3. Variables

Please note that variables are case-sensitive.

Use underscores instead of camelcase.

You can specify variables inside the metdata for a template. For example.

```
---
fruit: orange
---

That fruit is an {{fruit}}.
```

Will be rendered as:

That fruit is an orange.

